The algorithms come from this article:

https://www.polygon.com/2018/8/7/17660344/animal-crossing-letter-system-game-design-explained

I have attempted to write the rules to the algorithm in code but they seem to be a little off currently. Maybe I'm misinterpreting them.

If you happen to fix a mistake and want to share it please format your code similar to mine, comment it, and make a pull request.
